  - name: Boy
    sprite: {fileID: 6544739967473787804, guid: 852008989b0ae8b44b2da0e02283531f, type: 3}
    description: "\u0160is t\u0113ls att\u0113lots neitr\u0101l\u0101 poz\u0101 ar
      vienk\u0101r\u0161u ap\u0123\u0113rbu, kas kalpo k\u0101 pamats da\u017E\u0101diem
      t\u0113rpiem. Vi\u0146am ir tum\u0161i, nedaudz izsp\u016Bru\u0161i mati un
      p\u0101rliecin\u0101ta, mier\u012Bga izteiksme."
  - name: Girl
    sprite: {fileID: -5802829245062863535, guid: 8a3a977dd250cec4f8ed9bbdc65dad3a, type: 3}
    description: "Vi\u0146ai ir gai\u0161i, vi\u013C\u0146aini mati un draudz\u012Bga
      sejas izteiksme. Neitr\u0101lais ap\u0123\u0113rbs \u013Cauj viegli kombin\u0113t
      da\u017E\u0101dus t\u0113rpus un aksesu\u0101rus. T\u0113ls ir piem\u0113rots
      da\u017E\u0101diem stiliem \u2013 no ikdieni\u0161\u0137a l\u012Bdz fant\u0101zijas
      vai piedz\u012Bvojumu tematikai."
